A couple of years ago, I was bothered by this reference in Fred
Cohen's papers, since the page numbers given don't exist in any 1974
issue of ACM communications, so I tracked this paper down.  The paper
appeared in ACM SIGAPL: APL QuoteQuad, V. 14, No. 4, pages 163-168
